Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「共結山盟誓…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是
