Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「靜夜待子規…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是空牌
