Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:57.52,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「春深帶雨長 朱櫻哀色衰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續七張空牌!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手誤…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有忍住呢 Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 送給你的牌就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
